flowRoot.flowPara: Your first visit to the space is free!
For further visists we recommend a £4 donation.
Visitors are welcome during regular opening hours and events.
Friends are “pay-as-you-go” users of the makerspace.
Register for free on our website:
This gives you access to our online Members' Area.
Supporters pay a monthly subscription to help So Make It grow.
A subscription includes access to the space whenever a keyholder is present.
Members are the backbone of the space, keeping it running smoothly, running workshops, and much more.
Members can vote on decisions affecting the makerspace.
Keyholders can open the space at any time.
Keyholders are known and approved by the community.
Trustees are the directors of So Make It Ltd.
Trustees get to fill out all the paperwork.
